  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆ Synopsis ◆</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Does every romance have to end in marriage or breakup?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Is a life without marriage or children the key to true happiness?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether or not you've ever been in love,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >you’ve surely heard countless perspectives on romance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, you’ll play as a woman who is in a relationship.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When your ex, current partner, and first love each begin to stir your heart,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >how will the tangled threads of love shape your destiny?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into this trial of love</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and uncover the ending that truly belongs to you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆ Character Introduction ◆</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >李承舜 ( Ex-Partner )</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365970/extras/4de3a30766fae5d53fe24f3382d857f2.avif?t=1735920764\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365970/extras_big/4de3a30766fae5d53fe24f3382d857f2.avif?t=1735920764 width=800 height=426 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高博仁（ First Love ）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365970/extras/61f96d72f2be22cd477e3159fafbf839.avif?t=1735920764\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365970/extras_big/61f96d72f2be22cd477e3159fafbf839.avif?t=1735920764 width=800 height=426 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >曾宇翔（ Current Partner )</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365970/extras/870fef7d5294a9b37c537178e0e25a2b.avif?t=1735920764\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365970/extras_big/870fef7d5294a9b37c537178e0e25a2b.avif?t=1735920764 width=800 height=426 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆ Key Features ◆</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choices Affect the Ending: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every decision you make will shape the direction of your story, offering a variety of possible outcomes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique Male Lead Storylines: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each male lead has a unique, heartfelt storyline that keeps you coming back for more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exploring the Truths of Love: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A genuine portrayal of the struggles and choices within love, offering resonance and reflection.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆ Synopsis ◆</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Does every romance have to end in marriage or breakup?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Is a life without marriage or children the key to true happiness?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether or not you've ever been in love,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >you’ve surely heard countless perspectives on romance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, you’ll play as a woman who is in a relationship.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When your ex, current partner, and first love each begin to stir your heart,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >how will the tangled threads of love shape your destiny?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into this trial of love</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and uncover the ending that truly belongs to you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆ Character Introduction ◆</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >李承舜 ( Ex-Partner )</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365970/extras/4de3a30766fae5d53fe24f3382d857f2.avif?t=1735920764\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365970/extras_big/4de3a30766fae5d53fe24f3382d857f2.avif?t=1735920764 width=800 height=426 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高博仁（ First Love ）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365970/extras/61f96d72f2be22cd477e3159fafbf839.avif?t=1735920764\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365970/extras_big/61f96d72f2be22cd477e3159fafbf839.avif?t=1735920764 width=800 height=426 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >曾宇翔（ Current Partner )</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365970/extras/870fef7d5294a9b37c537178e0e25a2b.avif?t=1735920764\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365970/extras_big/870fef7d5294a9b37c537178e0e25a2b.avif?t=1735920764 width=800 height=426 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆ Key Features ◆</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choices Affect the Ending: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every decision you make will shape the direction of your story, offering a variety of possible outcomes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique Male Lead Storylines: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each male lead has a unique, heartfelt storyline that keeps you coming back for more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exploring the Truths of Love: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A genuine portrayal of the struggles and choices within love, offering resonance and reflection.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
